title: The Many-Faced Azor Ahai (Con Panel Audio)
description:
From the "Aziz forgot to publish this" category, recorded back at Con of Thrones 2019.

It's a panel where Ash and Aziz entertained the notion that Azor Ahai might be many figures instead of one.
